    },
    {
      "title": "Cut and Attach Side Rails",
      "body": "In order to get the two side rail supports (1 1/2\" x 1 3/4\" x 22 3/4\") use a table saw to rip a 2x4 cut to 22 3/4\" in half. Attach as shown using 2 1/2\" outdoor wood screws.",
